A '''skeletal miner''' is an [[undead]] monster. It appears on the second and 4th level of the [[Abandoned Mine]] as a corpse with the examine text "Well, at least he doesn't have to worry about getting 'black lung'." and will animate occasionally when walked past to attack you. It counts as a [[skeleton]] for the purpose of [[Slayer]] [[Slayer task|tasks]].
[[File:Skeletal Miner Corpse.png|thumb|The Skeletal Miner as a "Corpse"]]

